title: Home | 首頁
content: Bridging the gap - Spanning the world. Through the Power of Design. We are SEFBO, a collective of architects, designers, and thinkers. Design with purpose, build for the future. SEFBO 是一家跨領域的設計公司，我們相信卓越的設計能夠塑造更美好的世界。我們專注於建築、室內與品牌策略，為客戶提供兼具前瞻性與永續性的解決方案。

title: Our Projects | 專案作品
content: 從商業地標到文化空間，我們的作品遍及全球，每一個專案都承載著我們對品質、創新與在地文化的承諾。Corporate Headquarters, Commercial & Office Building, City Art Museum, Cultural & Public Space, Lakeside Residence, Residential Complex Design, Soundscape Concert Hall, Entertainment & Arts. Austin, Texas, 重慶, 中國, 北京, Lhasa, Tibet.

title: About Us & Team | 關於我們與團隊
content: We are a collective of architects, designers, and thinkers, united by a shared passion for creating spaces that inspire. Meet The Team. Johnathan Doe, Founder & Principal Architect. Jane Smith, Head of Interior Design. Peter Jones, Director of Brand Strategy.

content: Have a project in mind? Let's work together to bring your vision to life. We're ready to listen. Name, Email, Message, Send Message.
